snippet.title: Yes, Your Grace Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy Yes, Your Grace on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1115690/Yes_Your_Grace/

In this Kingdom management RPG, petitioners will arrive in the throne room to ask for your guidance. Decide whether to intervene with their problems or conserve resources.

A huge thank you to Merkfolk for supplying music for the trailer: http://www.merkfolk.pl

Developed by Brave At Night
Published by No More Robots
